1. 作用

为了解决classification问题

2. 算法概述

2.1 traning

step1: take all features of every example and multiply each one by a weight 
andadd them up

step2: This result of step1 will be put into the sigmoid

step3: for the output of step2, anything above 0.5 will calssified as a 1, and anything below 0.5 will be classified as a 0

step4: 

2.2 sigmoid function

At 0 the value of the sigmoid is 0.5. For increasing values of x, the sigmoid will approach 1 and for decreasing values of x, the sigmoid will approach 0. 

3.plot boundary

在sigmoid函数的变量中

>0 时，sigmoid输出

>0.5此时被认为1

变量<0, sigmoid输出

<0.5,则被分类为0,

所以wx=0时，被认为是分界线

书中的的plotbestfit函数很很值得学习
